column1: If numeric kdti greater than 21 OR ( categorical rldu equal to 1 AND numeric ahyp greater than 30 ) , then it is normally 2.
If categorical pvof equal to 2 , then it is sometimes Not Qualified.
If numeric ahyp greater than or equal to 2 AND categorical gcaj equal to 1 , then it is certainly 3.
If categorical gcaj equal to 5 AND ( categorical pvof equal to 3 OR categorical rldu equal to 5 ) , then it is often 4.
